                            <comment id="13400872" author="jmspaggi" created="Mon, 25 Jun 2012 20:43:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Bryce,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So what you are saying is that you used this example instead?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt; 
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;?xml version=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;1.0&quot;&lt;/span&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;?xml-stylesheet type=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;text/xsl&quot;&lt;/span&gt; href=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;configuration.xsl&quot;&lt;/span&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;configuration&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;property&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;name&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;hbase.rootdir&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/name&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &amp;lt;!-- Depending on your platform, this may create a &apos;file:&apos; directory
         in hbase home instead of the desired behavior. Try using a standard
         platform specific absolute path instead. --&amp;gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;value&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;/DIRECTORY/hbase&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; 

&lt;p&gt;On a fully-distributed environment, it should be something like &quot;hdfs://...&quot;. But &quot;file://...&quot; should still be working even under linux. At least, it was worling for me. Are you sure there is no typo? Can you give it another try? I will retry too on my side.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13443393" author="jesse_yates" created="Tue, 28 Aug 2012 18:55:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Closing as invalid. Reoopen if I&apos;m mistaken.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
